{"tid":1703260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳浩天：我好仁慈，但國際上有堆貌似反中，其實係間諜操控","createTime":"2019-11-10T07:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T09:33:48.000Z","uid":133680,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"612d1d8d9d9f1f7891bd1b33a7ca69d477bc466c","tid":1703260,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:49:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10158948373910130&amp;id=690555129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10158948373910130%26id%3D690555129&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWIVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=bf5eda5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10158948373910130&amp;id=690555129</a><br />\n<br />\n我都好少篤爆人，從來遇到鬼我都唔會當面拆穿，不過而家關鍵時刻，為大家安全著想，我善意提醒一下大家。國際上有堆貌似反中，或者支持中國民主化嘅組織，實際上由間諜/雙面間諜操控。<br />\n<br />\n其實我係咪太仁慈呢？邊啲人邊啲鬼一直心裏有數，但從來冇公開處刑。你地搵食還搵食，收風賣料就算喇，唔好搞咁多野。<br />\n<br />\nPs 台灣鬼會唔會睇唔明呢？台灣鬼似乎多過香港鬼，多到嚇死人。"},{"pid":"9808940d706792209cdfc60c1ad8ec0bd99c8325","tid":1703260,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:55:58.000Z","msg":"［預言］涉強姦警員會孭起整隊警隊罪行，並可能全家被滅口<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1701986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1701986</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c6978e27e842d4348a4a597a4a7f085cb0984c7","tid":1703260,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb4cd0f15104d766d076b5fbdd9be8506cfb6a4","tid":1703260,"uid":21275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"385c4ed0e2eca3bdc4ca548bc502d05c3fd127bb","tid":1703260,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3df5e0285e01d06545a3e